description:
Gully Boys perform at The Current Presents: Minnesota Music Month
Support The Current: https://support.mpr.org/youtube

The Current hosted Minnesota Music Month back in April, 2025 at Amsterdam Bar & Hall featuring Gully Boys, Bad Bad Hats, Kiss the Tiger, and Lighter Co. 

Watch Gully Boys’ full performance above. 

Songs Performed
00:00:00 Bad Day
00:03:05 Optimist
00:06:47 See You See
00:11:08 Love Me 2
00:14:03 The Way
00:17:33 Favorite Son
00:22:15 Shame
00:25:01 Break
00:28:36 Spit
00:31:02 Mother

Musicians
Kathy Callahan: vocals, guitar
Natalie Klemond: bass, vocals
Nadirah McGill: drums, vocals
Mariah Mercedes: lead guitar

Credits
